modules.description: Provides functions to record, play, and stop audio files using device media capabilities. Works with file paths, media IDs, and playback durations. Enables voice memo recording and audio playback in mobile applications.

Provides functions to control and query media playback, including playing, pausing, stopping, seeking, and adjusting volume. Works with media objects and error handling through custom types for status and error states. Enables real-time amplitude monitoring, recording initiation, and duration retrieval in audio applications.
